title: I like to party
name: I like to party
description:
A Map by Baostar

Places to get things for your next party.

properties.name: All American Party Rentals
properties.description: Posted by Baostar 2199 N Batavia St Ste B, Orange, CA 92865Highly recommended by friends who\'ve have used them for movie projectors.

properties.name: Dippin' Dots
properties.description: Posted by Baostar   5101 Charter 18011 Newhope Street, Suite D, Fountain Valley, CAYou can get a whopping 30 servings tub of Delicious Dippin\' Dots for party with flavors like banana split, cotton candy, mint chocolate, and peanut butter chip.

properties.name: French's Cupcake Bakery
properties.description: Posted by Baostar273 E. 17th Street, Costa Mesa, CA 92627Family owned and operated by Jerry and Dianne French. They offer a mind-boggling range of cakes, and most of their cakes are one of a kind. We got birthday cakes from them from the past and they were simply delicious!

properties.name: Inkwells Paperie
properties.description: Posted by Baostar 3411 E. Coast Highway, Corona del Mar, CAYou won\'t find the typical greeting cards with puppies and sunsets here. Since buying card-and-gift shop Inkwells Paperie in July, former surf industry executive Raili Clasen has augmented the hip selection to include leather journals from Jonathan Adler and fancy gardening gloves by Hable Construction (started by former Kate Spade employees). Wrap up your gifts with one of the shop\'s intricate, feathered ribbons.

properties.name: Posta Chica

properties.name: SweetCake
properties.description: Posted by Baostar5825 West Sunset Boulevard, Suite 112, Hollywood, CASweetCake provides exquisite homemade pastries for caterers and restaurants, and, now, for at-home diners. The Small Bites menu includes quaint lemon meringue tartlets with shortbread crust, tiny bittersweet chocolate boxes with chocolate ganache and cashew caramel, and chic French macaroons in lemon, pistachio, or raspberry - can lend you the gourmet flair you\'re after. And once you try the cookies and custard shooters and see how easy it is to order them for your next cocktail party. Tastings at the private kitchen on Sunset are encouraged, so make an appointment to try some. You’ll find that they taste as good as they look.

properties.name: Tall Mouse Arts & Crafts
properties.description: Posted by Baostar 5695 Alton Pkwy, Irvine, CATall Mouse carries all kinds of things for parties and crafts and a bit more upscale than Michael\'s or Joanne\'s.

properties.name: Wonderland Bakery
properties.description: Posted by Baostar1314 Bison, Newport Beach, CAA new and enchanted bakery that opened across from The Bluffs in Newport Beach.
